LanguageData.VomitedCum.label: 呕吐精液
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.2: image->[PAWN_nameFull] 看起来昏昏沉沉，满身精液 [circumstance_group]
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.3: image->[PAWN_nameFull] 翻身并将精液干呕到地板上 [circumstance_group]
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.4: image->[PAWN_nameFull] 跪在 [PAWN_possessive] 膝盖上，在地板上呕吐精液 [circumstance_group]
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.7: desc_sentence->[PAWN_pronoun] 似乎完全不知道 [PAWN_objective] 周围有什么。
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.9: desc_sentence->[PAWN_pronoun] 几乎失去意识，[PAWN_possessive] 舌头伸出，精液从 [PAWN_possessive] 嘴里滴落。
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.12: desc_sentence->[PAWN_pronoun] 似乎想笑，尽管情况如此。
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.13: desc_sentence->[PAWN_pronoun] 看起来几乎泄了气，好像被剧烈的精液呕吐完全排空了。
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.14: desc_sentence->[PAWN_pronoun] 被艺术渲染的精液光环包围。
LanguageData.VomitedCum.rulePack.rulesStrings.15: desc_sentence->一只[动物]正在吃背景中的精液。
